A zombie wielding a bronze hatchet could be encountered during the Temple Trekking minigame, during the bridge puzzle event, prior to its rework in 2011. The zombie was guaranteed to drop a bronze hatchet when killed, which could be used to cut the nearby trees for logs to fill the gaps in the bridge.
